<div class="post top clearfix" >
    <h2 class="title">
        <a href="http://aaroncollins.org/?p=20"><span>The First $500 Tip!  </span></a>
    </h2>

        
                            <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <object width="1030" height="579"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/jP-TOI1mO0A?version=3&amp;hl=en_US"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/jP-TOI1mO0A?version=3&amp;hl=en_US" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="1030" height="579" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>                </div>
                    <div id="post" class="hasSidebar clearfix">
            <p>Yesterday our family went to Puccini&#8217;s in Lexington to give a $500 tip and make Aaron&#8217;s wish come true.  After the video she walked back to the kitchen and seemed to be telling everyone.  When she came back out we spoke off camera for a few minutes and she was kind enough to take a couple pictures with mom.</p>
<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/Hh2wF.jpg"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/ZTbyk.jpg"></p>
<p>We have already received over $500 more, so we will be doing this again soon.  Hopefully we can continue changing the lives of random waiters and waitresses for years.<br />
<center></p>
