        <p>I didn&#8217;t know Aaron, but I saw a post about this on Facebook from a friend.  I have been in the service industry for almost ten years, and I can tell you how under appreciated many of those in this field are.  We have kids, school, medical bills, and all the other things that take money that we sometimes just can&#8217;t seem to make enough of.  This kind of thing can really change people&#8217;s lives for the better.  I don&#8217;t currently have the extra cash to donate, but when I do, I plan to.  Keep it up!  I&#8217;m sure your brother would be proud!</p>

